<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>AI Chat UI</title>

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:#000;
    height:100vh;
    display:flex;
    overflow:hidden;
}

/* Left Sidebar */
.sidebar{
    width:110px;
    background:#000;
    border-right:4px solid #333;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:flex-start;
    padding-top:20px;
}

/* Hamburger */
.menu{
    cursor:pointer;
}

.menu div{
    width:70px;
    height:10px;
    background:white;
    margin:10px 0;
    border-radius:3px;
}

/* Main Area */
.main{
    flex:1;
    padding:10px;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
}

/* AI Response */
.response{
    flex:1;
    background:#9c9c9c;
    border-radius:28px;
    margin:0 20px 15px;
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
    padding:25px;
    overflow-y:auto;
}

/* Chat bubbles */
.bubble{
    max-width:75%;
    padding:15px 20px;
    margin:10px 0;
    border-radius:25px;
    font-size:20px;
    line-height:1.4;
}

.ai{
    background:#d9d9d9;
    color:#000;
    align-self:flex-start;
}

.user{
    background:#5d9cff;
    color:white;
    align-self:flex-end;
}

/* Input Box */
.input{
    height:105px;
    background:#9c9c9c;
    border-radius:28px;
    margin:0 20px 20px;
    display:flex;
    align-items:flex-start;
    padding:18px;
}

.input textarea{
    width:100%;
    height:100%;
    border:none;
    background:transparent;
    resize:none;
    outline:none;
    font-size:24px;
    color:black;
}

.input textarea::placeholder{
    color:black;
    font-weight:bold;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="sidebar">
    <div class="menu">
        <div></div>
        <div></div>
        <div></div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="main">

    <div class="response">

        <div class="bubble user">
            Hello!
        </div>

        <div class="bubble ai">
            Hi! How can I help you today?
        </div>

        <div class="bubble user">
            Can you explain AI?
        </div>

        <div class="bubble ai">
            Sure! Artificial Intelligence is software that can understand,
            reason, and generate responses based on information it has learned.
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="input">
        <textarea placeholder="input"></textarea>
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
